265
00:25:59.700 --> 00:26:03.746
Was the kidnapper just a total stranger?

266
00:26:05.623 --> 00:26:06.624
Yeah.

267
00:26:11.629 --> 00:26:13.339
I'd never seen him in my life.

268
00:26:15.341 --> 00:26:16.342
Ah.

269
00:26:18.010 --> 00:26:19.595
Wow.

270
00:26:21.764 --> 00:26:24.600
I mean. that's just unbelievable.

271
00:26:25.643 --> 00:26:29.981
How can someone be so horrible?
It's like something out of a movie.

272
00:26:30.690 --> 00:26:31.732
I know.

273
00:26:35.319 --> 00:26:36.362
I wish they'd die.

274
00:26:36.904 --> 00:26:38.698
I'm so hungry.

275
00:26:41.617 --> 00:26:43.327
Those people should be killed.

276
00:26:43.911 --> 00:26:46.122
Those disgusting vermin
don't deserve to live.

277
00:26:50.751 --> 00:26:53.296
Ah. Gosh. I totally forgot.

278
00:26:53.921 --> 00:26:54.964
You can use my phone.

279
00:26:57.049 --> 00:27:00.219
- Oh. I'm so sorry.
- No. it's fine.

280
00:27:26.829 --> 00:27:29.540
Seriously. I'm starving.

281
00:27:32.668 --> 00:27:34.003
Maybe kimchi stew.

282
00:27:44.764 --> 00:27:46.766
BABY ON BOARD
61K 9024

283
00:28:37.021 --> 00:28:38.022
Hi. Ms. Ko.

284
00:28:39.857 --> 00:28:42.651
How could you just take off
without saying bye?

285
00:28:43.402 --> 00:28:44.403
You hurt my feelings.

286
00:28:48.282 --> 00:28:49.283
Tell me.

287
00:28:50.618 --> 00:28:53.037
Did you seriously think
you could get away?

288
00:28:55.122 --> 00:28:56.957
You wanted to leave that badly?

289
00:30:08.028 --> 00:30:09.905
Let me show you a way out.

290
00:31:03.667 --> 00:31:05.294
Honey. stop it.

291
00:31:08.464 --> 00:31:12.801
Why did you start without me?
I didn't give you permission.

292
00:31:17.056 --> 00:31:18.891
She wanted out.

293
00:31:18.974 --> 00:31:23.103
I get it. but now's not the time.

294
00:31:23.187 --> 00:31:25.105
You can't be so impulsive about this.

295
00:31:25.189 --> 00:31:27.691
Oh my. Look at you.

296
00:31:34.782 --> 00:31:35.866
Are you okay?

297
00:31:37.242 --> 00:31:40.329
Thank goodness I came back in time.

298
00:31:41.413 --> 00:31:43.874
My husband has a short fuse.

299
00:31:44.541 --> 00:31:45.709
You all right?

300
00:31:47.544 --> 00:31:49.421
Now.

301
00:31:50.130 --> 00:31:53.300
Okay. Breathe.

302
00:31:55.636 --> 00:31:57.763
Keep doing that.

303
00:32:01.225 --> 00:32:03.143
Oh. you feeling any better?

304
00:32:03.727 --> 00:32:05.437
Who the hell are you?

305
00:32:06.689 --> 00:32:08.565
What do you mean? It's me.

306
00:32:09.316 --> 00:32:11.485
Oh. Do you not recognize me?

307
00:32:14.989 --> 00:32:16.699
Ah!

308
00:32:16.782 --> 00:32:18.117
Shh!

309
00:32:18.200 --> 00:32:21.620
Be quiet! You'll get us both in trouble!

310
00:32:23.831 --> 00:32:24.832
Oh.

311
00:32:27.876 --> 00:32:29.211
Are you okay?

312
00:32:30.963 --> 00:32:32.297
Are you hurt at all?

313
00:32:32.881 --> 00:32:35.509
You must be pretty confused.

314
00:32:36.218 --> 00:32:37.219
Who the hell are you?

315
00:32:37.845 --> 00:32:41.473
Don't make loud noises.
You'll be in trouble.

316
00:32:42.141 --> 00:32:43.809
What the hell are you saying?

317
00:32:44.435 --> 00:32:45.561
Shh!

318
00:32:46.228 --> 00:32:47.563
Be quiet!

319
00:32:47.646 --> 00:32:49.690
You'll get us both in trouble!

320
00:32:51.900 --> 00:32:53.861
Excuse me. what did you just say?

321
00:32:54.486 --> 00:32:57.614
We'll get in trouble
with the guy who locked us up here.

322
00:32:57.698 --> 00:32:59.992
Are you locked up
against your will too?

323
00:33:00.492 --> 00:33:01.493
What the…

324
00:33:02.077 --> 00:33:04.872
Damn it. I screwed up.

325
00:33:06.582 --> 00:33:08.125
Hey. Seyun.

326
00:33:08.751 --> 00:33:11.003
When you get out of here.

327
00:33:11.086 --> 00:33:14.631
can you let the police know…

328
00:33:16.341 --> 00:33:20.804
that Lee Seonja from Songmu-dong
died in this place?

329
00:33:23.557 --> 00:33:24.975
Oh. for crying out loud.

330
00:33:28.645 --> 00:33:30.189
Ms. Lee Seonja?

331
00:33:31.565 --> 00:33:33.650
Yeah. it's me.

332
00:33:33.734 --> 00:33:35.235
Remember me now?

333
00:34:39.007 --> 00:34:40.134
SERVICE LOG

334
00:35:08.036 --> 00:35:09.830
RESIDENT REGISTRATION CARD
HEO JAEIL

335
00:35:10.622 --> 00:35:11.707
"Heo Jaeil."

336
00:35:12.791 --> 00:35:14.793
RESIDENT REGISTRATION CARD
HEO JAEIL

337
00:35:23.510 --> 00:35:26.638
<i>Well. I just happened to be</i>
<i>in the area. so I got here fast.</i>

338
00:35:28.807 --> 00:35:30.642
All right. we're moving out.

339
00:35:30.726 --> 00:35:32.686
…and let's see
how you feel by then.

340
00:35:33.812 --> 00:35:34.813
Okay. thank you.

341
00:35:35.772 --> 00:35:36.773
No.

342
00:35:46.658 --> 00:35:48.160
Who are you people?

343
00:35:48.827 --> 00:35:50.245
Have a seat.

344
00:35:50.913 --> 00:35:53.749
What is it that you want from me?

345
00:35:54.458 --> 00:35:55.918
Why are you doing this to me?

346
00:35:57.836 --> 00:36:00.756
You're not here
because we wanted you here.

347
00:36:02.174 --> 00:36:03.842
What's that supposed to mean?

348
00:36:03.926 --> 00:36:06.720
This is what your husband wanted.

349
00:36:06.803 --> 00:36:08.805
You know this already.

350
00:36:08.889 --> 00:36:10.515
Why do you keep acting dumb?

351
00:36:11.600 --> 00:36:12.601
Honey.

352
00:36:13.602 --> 00:36:16.605
Ms. Ko. I told you already.

353
00:36:17.231 --> 00:36:19.691
Mr. Kang put me up to all of it.

354
00:36:19.775 --> 00:36:21.652
No. that's a lie.

355
00:36:22.277 --> 00:36:23.487
I don't believe you.

356
00:36:23.570 --> 00:36:27.407
You must be in denial. huh?

357
00:36:33.288 --> 00:36:34.289
Oh. my back.

358
00:36:35.165 --> 00:36:36.333
<i>But you know.</i>

359
00:36:36.416 --> 00:36:40.379
<i>- there's a limit to how much you can lie.</i>
- Here. Look.

360
00:36:40.921 --> 00:36:46.218
<i>So I said we should get divorced.</i>

361
00:36:46.301 --> 00:36:50.389
<i>But she said she didn't want to.
Well. she said she'd never do it.</i>

362
00:36:55.352 --> 00:36:58.188
But h-h-how could this be?

363
00:36:59.648 --> 00:37:00.649
Who is this guy?

364
00:37:11.326 --> 00:37:13.245
It can't be.

365
00:37:24.965 --> 00:37:29.553
Seyun…

366
00:37:30.679 --> 00:37:31.805
Seyun…

367
00:37:34.850 --> 00:37:39.187
<i>I want you to get rid of my wife.</i>

368
00:37:40.647 --> 00:37:41.982
<i>What? What did you say?</i>

369
00:37:42.858 --> 00:37:44.526
<i>Get rid of my wife.</i>

370
00:37:47.195 --> 00:37:48.530
Ms. Ko.

371
00:37:49.990 --> 00:37:51.408
How does that make you feel?

372
00:37:54.036 --> 00:37:55.662
I know this is fake.

373
00:37:59.624 --> 00:38:01.752
There's no way he said anything like that.

374
00:38:02.377 --> 00:38:04.421
I know you don't want to believe it.

375
00:38:04.504 --> 00:38:05.505
But hey.

376
00:38:06.298 --> 00:38:12.054
You already know
that your husband doesn't love you.

377
00:38:15.682 --> 00:38:17.059
<i>Let's put an end to this.</i>

378
00:38:17.142 --> 00:38:18.143
What?

379
00:38:19.061 --> 00:38:20.062
I want a divorce.

380
00:38:25.192 --> 00:38:27.277
Hey. are you crying?

381
00:38:27.361 --> 00:38:29.738
Oh. no. She's crying.

382
00:38:29.821 --> 00:38:33.075
Oh. no. Poor thing.

383
00:38:40.791 --> 00:38:42.959
Hold me.

384
00:39:45.313 --> 00:39:47.607
PRINTER AND DIGITAL COPIER
RENTAL. SALES. AND REPAIR

385
00:40:07.586 --> 00:40:09.421
Okay. thank you.

386
00:40:11.298 --> 00:40:13.592
All right. we're moving out.

387
00:40:27.439 --> 00:40:29.065
They were colleagues.

388
00:40:33.320 --> 00:40:36.531
April 17.

389
00:40:38.617 --> 00:40:40.494
April 17.

390
00:40:43.622 --> 00:40:48.335
April 17…

391
00:40:48.919 --> 00:40:50.962
"Heo. Noh."

392
00:40:52.047 --> 00:40:53.298
"Heo…"

393
00:40:54.799 --> 00:40:56.218
"Noh."

394
00:40:56.301 --> 00:40:57.552
"Noh."

395
00:41:12.817 --> 00:41:15.403
RESIDENT REGISTRATION CARD
NOH MANHUI

396
00:41:16.863 --> 00:41:17.989
"Noh Manhui."

397
00:42:08.790 --> 00:42:10.458
Will you be my boyfriend?

398
00:42:25.849 --> 00:42:27.350
Wow.

399
00:42:29.227 --> 00:42:31.104
- Whoo! Go on. blow it out!
- Whoo! Come on! Blow it out!

400
00:42:33.231 --> 00:42:34.566
Good job!

401
00:42:35.191 --> 00:42:37.652
One. two. three!

402
00:42:37.736 --> 00:42:39.070
- Cheese!
- Cheese.

403
00:42:46.411 --> 00:42:49.497
It's 21-5 Yangsan-ro.

404
00:42:50.332 --> 00:42:52.083
It's 21-5 Yangsan-ro.

405
00:43:01.301 --> 00:43:02.385
Mmm.

406
00:43:03.136 --> 00:43:05.388
Here.

407
00:43:08.516 --> 00:43:09.768
- Hey. honey?
- Yeah?

408
00:43:09.851 --> 00:43:11.144
Is this it?

409
00:43:11.227 --> 00:43:12.562
What?

410
00:43:14.022 --> 00:43:16.107
Nothing. it's just…

411
00:43:16.191 --> 00:43:19.861
Did you want grilled ribs or something
after you blew three billion?

412
00:43:19.944 --> 00:43:21.488
We had ribs?

413
00:43:22.697 --> 00:43:24.324
You don't have to eat. you know.

414
00:43:25.533 --> 00:43:27.243
I never said I didn't want to eat.

415
00:43:30.538 --> 00:43:31.998
You know…

416
00:43:33.124 --> 00:43:38.380
I checked out the garden out back.
and the whole thing's frozen solid.

417
00:43:38.963 --> 00:43:39.964
Already?

418
00:43:41.049 --> 00:43:43.176
It probably won't thaw until March.

419
00:43:44.094 --> 00:43:46.596
Seriously? That's so far away.

420
00:43:46.680 --> 00:43:49.432
That's exactly what I'm saying.
The freezer's packed.

421
00:43:50.225 --> 00:43:52.143
What if we chop them up real small?

422
00:43:52.227 --> 00:43:53.770
I said it's packed.

423
00:44:03.405 --> 00:44:04.406
Who is it?

424
00:44:06.449 --> 00:44:09.786
And by the way.
we might want to air out the basement.

425
00:44:10.745 --> 00:44:11.746
Does it still smell?

426
00:44:12.247 --> 00:44:14.499
I said I'm sensitive to smell.

427
00:44:14.582 --> 00:44:16.418
But I've already aired it out.

428
00:44:16.501 --> 00:44:18.753
You probably didn't do it properly.

429
00:44:19.462 --> 00:44:20.463
Mmm.

430
00:44:21.131 --> 00:44:23.550
Okay. I'll pick up some bleach.

431
00:44:23.633 --> 00:44:26.094
No way. Don't use bleach.

432
00:44:26.177 --> 00:44:27.887
Geez. you don't let me do anything.

433
00:44:27.971 --> 00:44:31.182
It stinks even more when the smells mix.
I've already told you.

434
00:44:32.892 --> 00:44:35.562
Okay. fine. I'll take care of it.

435
00:44:36.062 --> 00:44:39.065
- I'll pick up some peroxide or something.
- Yeah. there you go. hmm?

436
00:44:39.899 --> 00:44:41.526
- Hurry. or you'll be late.
- Okay.

437
00:44:42.652 --> 00:44:44.279
You like these. Have some more.

438
00:44:44.362 --> 00:44:46.030
Thanks.

439
00:44:55.832 --> 00:44:58.126
<i>You will soon arrive at your destination.</i>

440
00:45:27.405 --> 00:45:30.658
JANG DOSIK
SEONGJIN POLICE STATION

441
00:45:30.742 --> 00:45:31.868
MESSAGES

442
00:46:56.035 --> 00:46:58.413
Oh my God.

443
00:46:59.497 --> 00:47:00.665
Is Noh Manhui home?

444
00:47:02.292 --> 00:47:04.127
Wait. wha-what are you talking about?

445
00:47:10.508 --> 00:47:12.719
I'm asking. Is your husband home?

446
00:47:13.595 --> 00:47:16.514
No. H-He's not home right now.

447
00:47:16.598 --> 00:47:17.849
And my wife?

448
00:47:20.685 --> 00:47:21.769
Where's my wife?

449
00:47:23.104 --> 00:47:25.189
- Who are you talking abou--
- My wife. Ko Seyun!

450
00:47:27.025 --> 00:47:28.860
Where are you keeping her?

451
00:47:28.943 --> 00:47:31.487
I don't know. I don't know anything.

452
00:47:32.238 --> 00:47:34.991
Wait! I really have no idea!

453
00:47:35.074 --> 00:47:37.535
I don't know anything about that. Please!

454
00:47:43.291 --> 00:47:44.959
INCOMING CALL
MY BABY

455
00:47:45.585 --> 00:47:46.961
Hey. honey.

456
00:47:47.045 --> 00:47:48.379
<i>Sweetie.</i>

457
00:47:49.547 --> 00:47:51.215
Hey. what's wrong?

458
00:47:52.800 --> 00:47:54.010
<i>Mr. Noh.</i>

459
00:47:55.261 --> 00:47:57.347
<i>It's me. Kang Taeju.</i>

460
00:48:03.019 --> 00:48:04.062
Mr. Kang?

461
00:48:06.189 --> 00:48:08.358
Noh Manhui. I finally got your name.

462
00:48:09.025 --> 00:48:10.568
<i>What are you doing there?</i>

463
00:48:11.402 --> 00:48:15.448
Sweetie. he's got a re-real gu-gun on him.

464
00:48:17.575 --> 00:48:19.035
Wait. I…

465
00:48:19.619 --> 00:48:22.288
Look. Just hold on a moment.
I'm making my way there now.

466
00:48:22.372 --> 00:48:23.414
<i>If we could just talk…</i>

467
00:48:24.290 --> 00:48:25.917
<i>Honey! No!</i>

468
00:48:26.000 --> 00:48:29.253
Oh. no! No!

469
00:48:29.337 --> 00:48:31.297
Honey. are you shot?

470
00:48:37.011 --> 00:48:38.513
Next time. she will be.

471
00:48:41.432 --> 00:48:42.725
<i>Noh Manhui!</i>

472
00:48:44.268 --> 00:48:49.649
This man is literally holding a gun
to my head right now.

473
00:48:50.358 --> 00:48:51.651
You hear me?

474
00:48:55.989 --> 00:49:01.244
Mr. Kang! Please. Mr. Kang!
Please don't do this!

475
00:49:03.079 --> 00:49:04.122
Talk.

476
00:49:05.665 --> 00:49:07.417
Where is my wife?

477
00:51:00.186 --> 00:51:02.480
- Honey.
- Honey.

478
00:51:11.571 --> 00:51:12.905
Seyun. are you okay?

479
00:51:14.073 --> 00:51:15.491
Are you hurt anywhere?

480
00:51:18.244 --> 00:51:19.704
It's all over now. Let's go home.

481
00:51:21.706 --> 00:51:23.374
We have to get out of here.

482
00:51:23.875 --> 00:51:25.168
You think you can walk?

483
00:51:26.711 --> 00:51:27.712
Don't touch me.

484
00:51:29.338 --> 00:51:30.798
Keep your hands off me.

485
00:51:32.300 --> 00:51:33.301
What's wrong?

486
00:51:34.886 --> 00:51:37.013
How could you do this to me?

487
00:51:39.140 --> 00:51:40.766
What do you mean?

488
00:51:40.850 --> 00:51:42.393
I saw the video.

489
00:51:46.731 --> 00:51:49.025
Where you tell that guy to kill me.

490
00:51:52.403 --> 00:51:55.281
Oh. that?

491
00:51:56.532 --> 00:51:57.992
That's a huge misunderstanding.

492
00:51:59.118 --> 00:52:01.204
I can explain everything.

493
00:52:01.287 --> 00:52:05.124
but right now. we have to get out of here.
We'll talk once we're out. okay? I'll…

494
00:52:05.208 --> 00:52:06.209
No!

495
00:52:10.671 --> 00:52:12.632
We don't have time for this right now!

496
00:52:13.508 --> 00:52:14.926
Please.

497
00:52:15.801 --> 00:52:17.845
We have to get the hell out of here!

498
00:52:24.101 --> 00:52:25.102
Seyun.

499
00:52:26.521 --> 00:52:28.856
Seyun. you have to believe me.

500
00:52:29.524 --> 00:52:32.860
That video. It's all a misunderstanding.

501
00:52:32.944 --> 00:52:34.320
I can explain all of it.

502
00:52:35.112 --> 00:52:36.155
Seyun.

503
00:52:37.156 --> 00:52:38.491
I'm telling you the truth.

504
00:52:38.991 --> 00:52:40.159
Please.

505
00:52:40.243 --> 00:52:41.744
Please just believe me.

506
00:54:13.711 --> 00:54:14.712
Honey!

507
00:54:15.963 --> 00:54:19.216
Mr. Kang. What are you doing here?

508
00:54:19.300 --> 00:54:20.343
No!

509
00:54:21.761 --> 00:54:23.095
Goddamn it!

510
00:55:14.855 --> 00:55:16.941
- Taeju!
- Oh. honey!

511
00:55:17.817 --> 00:55:20.277
Honey!

512
00:55:20.361 --> 00:55:24.240
Are you okay? Look at me. You okay?

513
00:55:28.577 --> 00:55:31.163
Honey. look at me.

514
00:55:31.247 --> 00:55:33.040
Go after them already.

515
00:55:33.124 --> 00:55:34.792
I said. are you okay?

516
00:55:34.875 --> 00:55:36.252
Noh Manhui!

517
00:55:36.335 --> 00:55:38.295
Chase them down and kill them!

518
00:56:25.176 --> 00:56:26.218
Are you okay?

519
00:56:27.136 --> 00:56:28.220
Yeah.

520
00:56:29.555 --> 00:56:31.265
We're going to get out of here.

521
00:56:31.891 --> 00:56:34.894
And I'll clear up this misunderstanding.

522
00:56:36.395 --> 00:56:37.605
You just need to trust me.

523
00:57:30.115 --> 00:57:31.575
Se-Se-Seyun.

524
00:57:31.659 --> 00:57:33.869
Seyun? Seyun.

525
00:57:34.703 --> 00:57:35.704
Seyun!

526
00:57:41.836 --> 00:57:43.212
Seyun!

527
00:58:04.900 --> 00:58:06.819
Seyun.

528
00:58:06.902 --> 00:58:08.237
Seyun. come on.

529
00:58:08.320 --> 00:58:10.865
Seyun. Come on. Please.

530
00:58:10.948 --> 00:58:12.199
Seyun.

531
00:58:12.283 --> 00:58:14.076
Seyun. can you hear me?

532
00:58:15.244 --> 00:58:16.745
Hey. are you okay?

533
00:58:16.829 --> 00:58:19.456
Let's go. Come on. Seyun.

534
00:58:19.540 --> 00:58:20.541
Honey.

535
00:58:21.417 --> 00:58:22.418
Honey.

536
00:58:23.043 --> 00:58:25.212
Look out!

537
00:58:27.506 --> 00:58:32.344
THE HUSBAND

538
00:59:12.968 --> 00:59:14.511
{\an8}- Seyun!
- Don't move!

539
00:59:14.595 --> 00:59:15.596
{\an8}<i>Stop right there!</i>

540
00:59:15.679 --> 00:59:16.931
{\an8}<i>We've lost the suspect.</i>

541
00:59:17.014 --> 00:59:19.433
{\an8}Also. we've located a female</i>
<i>inside the suspect's residence</i>…

542
00:59:19.516 --> 00:59:21.435
{\an8}<i>Her legs will be</i>
<i>permanently paralyzed</i>

543
00:59:21.518 --> 00:59:22.853
{\an8}if she doesn't get surgery right now.</i>

544
00:59:22.937 --> 00:59:24.313
{\an8}She may even die.</i>

545
00:59:25.314 --> 00:59:28.692
{\an8}<i>So you're asking to have her</i>
<i>operated on at our hospital?</i>

546
00:59:28.776 --> 00:59:29.777
{\an8}That criminal?

547
00:59:29.860 --> 00:59:31.070
{\an8}<i>What's this guy's deal?</i>

548
00:59:31.153 --> 00:59:34.239
{\an8}<i>You messed with the wrong person.</i>

549
00:59:34.323 --> 00:59:36.408
{\an8}I will not let that surgery happen. Never!

550
00:59:36.492 --> 00:59:37.660
{\an8}<i>I'm doing this surgery.</i>

551
00:59:37.743 --> 00:59:40.537
{\an8}<i>I want the truth.</i>
<i>I want to know why they kidnapped me.</i>

552
00:59:40.621 --> 00:59:42.498
{\an8}<i>I'll operate on you.</i>

553
00:59:42.581 --> 00:59:44.166
{\an8}Don't worry. I'm a doctor.

554
00:59:44.667 --> 00:59:46.669
Translated by Hyun Sik Yoon

